Netizen contribution
In front of the Meishan Municipal Government in Sichuan Province, all owners of the Shigaochuan Port real estate project gathered to protest due to the developer's false propaganda in the early stage, demanding the developer to refund and return the house.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: The reasons why the owner requested to return the house: 1. The developer initially advertised the construction of an industrial park, but after the commercial housing was sold, the developer announced the withdrawal of investment, and the industrial park plan fell through. 2. The property is located in the Tianfu New District of Meishan, and many housing sales only advertised that it was in the Tianfu New District of Sichuan. Out-of-town buyers thought it was the Tianfu New District of Chengdu. At that time, the housing prices were very high (more than 10,000 yuan), and now the housing prices are around 7-8k, which is basically halved. 3. There are many quality problems with the new house, and the owner has no way to complain.

Recently, a recording of a Wuhan grandmother complaining about the medical insurance reform has been widely circulated among the elderly in Wuhan.
It is reported that the retired elderly originally had a monthly account of 260 yuan, but now it is only 83 yuan per month. On the surface, 4,000 yuan can be reimbursed per year, but the actual reimbursement amount is only 1,300 yuan.
And useful drugs are kicked out of medical insurance, and useless drugs can be reimbursed, which is equivalent to self-funded medical treatment in disguise.
